dct_description_sm: Lines representing roads, railways, runways, paths, ferries, and surface waters in Hong Kong for 1999. Multiple types of roads and railways are also distinguished. The data were extracted from a map by the Survey and Mapping Office of the Hong Kong Lands Department and published by LAND INFO Worldwide Mapping.
